  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On this tranquil island, you will manage your own farm. Grow crops, build facilities, and sell products to earn rent and drive farm growth. Accumulate wealth to purchase permanent land use rights and become the true owner of the farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Agriculture</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planting, watering, harvesting, and various other agricultural tasks. Transforming the lonely island into a beautiful farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/ca719b741e7e4c7ffbb2e865946f6be9.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/ca719b741e7e4c7ffbb2e865946f6be9.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/ca719b741e7e4c7ffbb2e865946f6be9.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breeding</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animal breeding, with a chance to breed rare breeds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/9b579b178eaed93af2b8051297ab4e2b.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/9b579b178eaed93af2b8051297ab4e2b.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/9b579b178eaed93af2b8051297ab4e2b.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Treasure chest</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While exploring the seabed, you discover a treasure chest! Open it and reap unexpected surprises!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/cd79cb9ec9649c966482987f633e2506.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/cd79cb9ec9649c966482987f633e2506.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/cd79cb9ec9649c966482987f633e2506.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock your unique achievements through activities such as planting crops, breeding animals, and fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/784bcc529dfd5699f102632ba7c8e870.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/784bcc529dfd5699f102632ba7c8e870.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/784bcc529dfd5699f102632ba7c8e870.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On this tranquil island, you will manage your own farm. Grow crops, build facilities, and sell products to earn rent and drive farm growth. Accumulate wealth to purchase permanent land use rights and become the true owner of the farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Agriculture</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planting, watering, harvesting, and various other agricultural tasks. Transforming the lonely island into a beautiful farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/ca719b741e7e4c7ffbb2e865946f6be9.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/ca719b741e7e4c7ffbb2e865946f6be9.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/ca719b741e7e4c7ffbb2e865946f6be9.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breeding</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animal breeding, with a chance to breed rare breeds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/9b579b178eaed93af2b8051297ab4e2b.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/9b579b178eaed93af2b8051297ab4e2b.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/9b579b178eaed93af2b8051297ab4e2b.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Treasure chest</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While exploring the seabed, you discover a treasure chest! Open it and reap unexpected surprises!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/cd79cb9ec9649c966482987f633e2506.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/cd79cb9ec9649c966482987f633e2506.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/cd79cb9ec9649c966482987f633e2506.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock your unique achievements through activities such as planting crops, breeding animals, and fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/784bcc529dfd5699f102632ba7c8e870.poster.avif?t=1767079370\" width=616 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/784bcc529dfd5699f102632ba7c8e870.webm?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771180/extras/784bcc529dfd5699f102632ba7c8e870.mp4?t=1767079370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
